title: For Sale/Trade:  Original Black Talon 45 ACP Ammo
postcontent: Up for sale is a box of 20 45 ACP Black Talon ammo. As you may know, it was removed from the market due to media falsely calling it armor piercing from the same lack of knowledge that threatens our second amendment today. The black talon ammo may not be armor piercing, but it certainly has that scary black finish on the bullet which is a lubalox coating to protect your barrel. When these rounds expand, their thicker than usual jacketing shreds into a star shape with several razor like talons. These were also taken off the market partially because the talons were a hazard to surgeons when being removed from patients. These rounds have some serious stopping power but are also seen as a collectible due to their contrverciality. Looking to get $60 for the box or trade.
